text: John Southworth (c. 1526 – 3 November 1595), of Samlesbury, Lancashire, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Lancashire in 1563. ==References== Category:1526 births Category:1595 deaths Category:English MPs 1563–1567 Category:Members of the Parliament of England (pre-1707) for Lancashire
